gurmukhi: ਅਗਾਧਿ ਬਿਅਾਧਿ ਨਾਸਨੰ || ਪਰੇਯੰ ਪਰਮ ੳੁਪਾਸਨੰ ||
transliteration: Agaddh(i) Biaadh(i) Naasanan|| Dareyan Param Oupaasanan||
translation: He is Unfathomable and destroyer of ailment; He is far beyond and supremely aborable.

gurmukhi: ਤ੍ਰਿਕਾਲ ਲੋਕ ਮਾਨ ਹੈਂ || ਸਦੈਵ ਪੁਰਖ ਪ੍ਰਧਾਨ ਹੈਂ ||
transliteration: Trikaal Lok Maan Hain|| Sadaiv Purakh Pradhaan Hain||6||14||
translation: He is worshipped by all in the past, present and future:He si always the Supreme Purusha. 6. 14.
Thou art of such attributes; Thou art of such attributes. PAUSE.

gurmukhi: ਕ੍ਰਿਪਾਲ ਦਿਅਾਲ ਕਰਮ ਹੈਂ || ਅਗੰਜ ਭੰਜ ਭਰਮ ਹੈਂ ||
transliteration: Kridaal Diaal Karam Hain|| Agadj Bhanj Bharam Hain||
translation: He, the merciful Lord performs actions of kindness; He is invincible and destroys illusions.

gurmukhi: ਤ੍ਰਿਕਾਲ ਲੋਕ ਪਾਲ ਹੈਂ || ਸਦੈਵ ਸਰਬ ਦਿਅਾਲ ਹੈਂ ||੭||੧੫||
transliteration: Trikaal Lok Paal Hain|| Sadaiv Sarab Diaal Hain||7||15||
translation: He is the Sustainer of people in past, present and future and is always compassionate towards all.7.15.
Therefore I repeat Thy Name, I repeat Thy Name.PAUSE.

gurmukhi: ਮਹਾਨ ਮੋਨ ਮਾਨ ਹੈਂ || ਪਰੇਵ ਪਰਮ ਪ੍ਰਧਾਨ ਹੈਂ ||
transliteration: Mahaan Mon Maan Hain|| Darev Param Radhaan Hain||
translation: He is Supreme in remaining peaceful; He is far beyond, superb and supreme.

gurmukhi: ਪੂਰਨ ਪ੍ਰੇਤ ਨਾਸਨੰ || ਸਦੈਵ ਸਰਬ ਪਾਸਨੰ ||੮||੧੬||
transliteration: Puraan Prêt Naasanan|| Sadaiv Sarab Paasanan||8||16||
translation: He is the destroyer of ghosts since ancient times and always abides with all.8.16.

gurmukhi: ਪ੍ਰਚੰਡ ਅਖੰਡ ਮੰਡਲੀ || ੳੁਦੰਡ ਰਾਜ ਸੁਥਲੀ ||
translation: The assembly is mighty and indivisible, Thy rule is fearless.

gurmukhi: ਜਗੰਤ ਜੋਤਿ ਜੁਅਾਲ ਕਾ || ਜਲੰਤ ਦੀਪ ਮਾਲਕਾ ||੯||੧੭||
transliteration: Jagadt Jot(i) Juaal Kaa|| Jalant Deep Maalkaa||9||17||
translation: The flame of Thy fire is illumined like the row of lamps.9.17.

gurmukhi: ਕ੍ਰਿਪਾਲ ਦਿਅਾਲ ਲੋਚਨੰ || ਮਚੰਕ ਬਾਣ ਮੋਚਨੰ ||
transliteration: Kridaal Diaal Lochanndng|| Machannd Baan Mochanndng||
translation: The eyes of the Merciful and Kind Lord humiliate the arrows of Cupaid.

gurmukhi: ਸਿਰੰ ਕਰੀਟ ਧਾਰੀਯੰ || ਦਿਨੇਸ ਕ੍ਰਿਤ ਹਾਰੀਯੰ ||੧੦||੧੮||
transliteration: Siran Dareet Dhdareeyan|| Dines Krit Hdareeyan||10||18||
translation: Thou art wearing such crown on Thy head which debases the pride of sum.10.18.

gurmukhi: ਬਿਸਾਲ ਲਾਲ ਲੋਚਨੰ || ਮਨੋਜ ਮਾਨ ਮੋਚਨੰ ||
transliteration: Bisaal Laal Lochanndng|| Manoj Maan Mochanndng||
translation: Thy wide and red eyes destroy the pride of Cupid.

gurmukhi: ਸੁਭੰਤ ਸੀਸ ਸੁ ਪ੍ਰਭਾ || ਚਕ੍ਰਿਤ ਚਾਰੁ ਚੰਦ੍ਰਕਾ ||੧੧||੧੯||
transliteration: Soubhant Sees Su Prabhaa|| Chakrit Chaar(u) Channdrakaa||11||19||
translation: The brilliance of the flame of Thy fire puzzles brightness of Thy Kingdom.
